      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   prs-dpm-snx-000      thru prs-dpm-snx-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/No gestione materiali vari attiva        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   prs-mtv-snx-000      thru prs-mtv-snx-999        .
       pre-exe-pgm-999.
