           move      "pgm/dpm[snx]"       to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           if        s-ves                =    spaces
                     move  s-alf          to   w-prs-dpm-snx
           else      move  "N"            to   w-prs-dpm-snx          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione personalizzazione               *
